OL,3,CInitial police investigation into
OL,4,CKatie Simpson death 'flawed', says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FThe Police Ombudsman investigation
OL,8,Fidentified breaches of the PSNI Code
OL,9,Fof Ethics in respect of professional
OL,10,Fduty, the conduct of police
OL,11,Finvestigations and the duty of
OL,12,Fsupervisors.
OL,14,FAs a result, disciplinary
OL,15,Frecommendations were made to the PSNI
OL,16,Fin respect of six police officers. No
OL,17,Faction was taken against three
OL,18,Fofficers, two of whom had retired and
OL,19,Fone for whom no misconduct was proven.
